Package: modexpress
Type: Package
Title: Express Model Coefficients and Diagnostics Along Variables Outside of the Model
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "William", "Chapman",
      email = "william.m.chapman@mail.mcgill.ca",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Methods for plotting and testing model coefficients and diagnostics
  to assess whether or not there is systematic variation within the model
  according to numeric or factor variables, whether or not they are
  used in the model itself.
